2013-03-11    <Olivier.Amann@swisslife.ch>

	* src/odbc-sql-functions.lisp: Adapted to the changes in src/odbc-sql-constants.lisp.

	* src/odbc-package.lisp: Added definition of the package "CH.AMANN-WOLOWYK.ODBC-SYSTEM-SQL-CONSTANTS" nicknamed "$" and containing SQL-constants.

	* src/odbc-sql-constants.lisp: Constants are external symbols of the package "CH.AMANN-WOLOWYK.ODBC-SYSTEM-SQL-CONSTANTS".

	* src/odbc-base.lisp: Defined Buffer objects as wrapper around a cffi:pointer on a foreign buffer. Columns and Parameters will contain such a buffer.

	* awl-odbc.asd (#:cl-user): Added files "odbc-ffi" and "odbc-sql-type-aliases" to the system.

